{{Quote|Ebaq Nine was once exploited by the Deep Core Mining Corporation for its deposits of bronzium. The moon was opened up shortly after the rise of Palpatine. During the war years the Empire maintained an observation post there, and used Ebaq Nine as an emergency resupply point, but the moon is now empty.|Gial Ackbar|<ref name="Way" />}} 
'''Deep Core Mining Corporation''' was a [[Mining/Legends|mining]] firm that operated on [[Planet/Legends|planets]] and [[Moon/Legends|moons]] in the [[Deep Core/Legends|Deep Core]], including mining [[Bronzium/Legends|bronzium]] on the moon of [[Ebaq 9]].

